feedback.title: Great Course!
feedback.body: This course was very informative and well-structured.

feedback.title: Excellent Instructor
feedback.body: The instructor explained concepts clearly and was very engaging.

feedback.title: Too Fast-Paced
feedback.body: The course moved too quickly for beginners to keep up.

feedback.title: Highly Recommend
feedback.body: I would highly recommend this course to anyone looking to learn Node.js.

feedback.title: Needs More Examples
feedback.body: The course could benefit from more practical examples and exercises.

feedback.title: Well Organized
feedback.body: The course content was well organized and easy to follow.

feedback.title: Great for Beginners
feedback.body: This course is perfect for beginners looking to get started with Node.js.

feedback.title: Could Use More Depth
feedback.body: While the course was good, it could use more depth on advanced topics.

feedback.title: Interactive and Fun
feedback.body: The interactive elements made learning fun and engaging.

feedback.title: Well Worth the Time
feedback.body: This course was well worth the time invested.
